>> source: https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/minestrone-minutes
>> time required: 10 minutes
>> image: https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/recipe-image-legacy-id-1202595_11-36e9761.jpg?resize=768,574

Bring the @stock{1%l} to the boil with the tomatoes, then add the @spaghetti{100%g} and cook for ~{6%min}s or until done. A few minutes before the pasta is ready, add the vegetables and bring back to the boil. Simmer for ~{2%min}s until everything is cooked.

Serve in bowls drizzled with @pesto{4%tbsp} and @oil{}, sprinkled with parmesan.
